mandatorySections

public java.util.Collection<ExpeditedReportSection> mandatorySections(ExpeditedAdverseEventReport aeReport,
                                                                      ReportDefinition... reportDefinitions)
                                                               throws java.lang.Exception
This method will find the mandatory sections defined, in the mandatory-section-rules, for a given report definition. Case 1: If report definitions is empy, the ExpeditedAdverseEventReport is scanned for active Reports, the ReportDefinition associated to each such report is considered. Case 2: If ReportDefinitions are passed explicitly, then will work against the report definitions instead.
